  "title": "Cafe Service Crew [ Part Time ]",
  "description": "<h2>Part-Time Staff Hiring (Korean Café – Bingsu Specialty)</h2><p>Hello,<br />We are hiring part-time service crew for a Korean café specializing in Bingsu (Korean shaved ice desserts).</p><h3><strong>Position       </strong>Part-Time Service Crew (1 person for each shift)</h3><h3><strong>Main Duties</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Customer service & table serving</p></li><li><p>Cleaning and maintaining hygiene</p></li><li><p>Simple beverage preparation</p></li></ul><h2><strong>Available Shifts</strong></h2><h3><strong>1) Night Shift (Thu/Fri/Sat/Sun)</strong></h3><ul><li><p><strong>10:00 PM – 1:00 AM (3 hours)</strong></p></li><li><p><strong>Monthly Salary: SGD 800</strong></p></li></ul><h3><strong>2) Day Shift (Sat/Sun)</strong></h3><ul><li><p><strong>12:00 PM – 6:00 PM (6 hours)</strong></p></li><li><p><strong>Monthly Salary: SGD 800</strong></p></li></ul><h2><strong>Requirements</strong></h2><ul><li><p>Minimum <strong>1 year of café experience</strong></p></li><li><p>Must hold a <strong>Food Hygiene Certificate</strong></p></li><li><p>Strong cleaning skills preferred</p></li><li><p><strong>PR / Singapore Citizen only</strong></p></li></ul><h2><strong>Additional Note</strong></h2><ul><li><p><strong>one free drink per day</strong> is available for staff</p></li></ul><h2><strong>Application</strong></h2><ul><li><p>Only <strong>one position available per shift</strong></p></li><li><p>Shortlisted candidates will be contacted individually for an interview</p></li><li><p>Applicants must be able to start work <strong>immediately from February</strong></p></li></ul><p><br />Please send your resume if interested<br />babnbingsoo@gmail.com </p><p>Thank you!</p>",
